Sources here are from lua-5.2.0 (http://www.lua.org/ftp/lua-5.2.0.tar.gz)
with all lua.org bugfixes (http://www.lua.org/bugs.html) as of 31-Mar-12
applied. This means patches 1 and 2.

Not entire lua distribution directory hierarchy is included here, and
some files needed for Freeciv usage have been added.
